<h1>Disable SIP ALG on ASUS routers.</h1>
<p class="lede">ASUS calls SIP ALG "SIP Passthrough." It's enabled by default on RT-AX, ZenWiFi, and ASUSWRT-based routers. Disable it before placing production traffic.</p>
